				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\hbox{Myr}$$\end{document} of [80]), because simulating with an N-body integrator thousands of planetary system over billion year-timescales is currently prohibitively expensive. In the subsequent ‘Evolution’ phase, the planets evolve individually to a 5 Gyr\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
