Class II are systems with more massive planets, yet no giants. There are usually 5 to 10 planets whose mass is larger than 1 M⊕\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
